  "name": "default",
  "description": "Default studio compositor layout \u2014 post-epic operator defaults. Reverie upper-right, Vitruvian Man (token_pole) upper-left, album lower-left, chat stats (stream_overlay) lower-right. These assignments are a starting point; Hapax content programming ultimately drives which sources feed which quadrants via the affordance pipeline + command registry. Phase 4/5 legibility surfaces added (activity_header, stance_indicator, chat_keyword_legend, grounding_provenance_ticker) per volitional-director epic \u00a73.5. Captions ward removed 2026-04-20 per operator (no captions on broadcast).",
